<p><span>2020年7月上海总体上牌数是<span>51,942<span>。较上月环比下降<span>3.92<span>％<span>，同比增长<span>10.46％<span>。<span>1-7月累计上牌数<span><span>259,678<span>，累计同比下降<span>10.96％<span>。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
